[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m559[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m for a more thorough validation, the presence of [0m[32m"begin"[0m[39m before [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPrivate[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m560[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m determines how code before and following charstrings should look[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m561[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m it is not currently checked anyway[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m562[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m563[0m[39m:            peekToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m564[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m565[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpeekToken == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m566[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m567[0m[39m:            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"/Private token not found"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m568[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Lexer.jav[0m[1;92ma:71[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m96[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m71[0m[39m:    public Token [0m[1;35mnextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m72[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m73[0m[39m:        Token curToken = aheadToken;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m74[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[95mSystem.out.println[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurToken[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m for debugging[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m75[0m[39m:        aheadToken = [0m[1;35mreadToken[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurToken[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m76[0m[39m:        return curToken;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m77[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m78[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m79[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m80[0m[39m:     * Returns the next token without consuming it.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m81[0m[39m:     * @return The next token[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m82[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m83[0m[39m:    public Token [0m[1;35mpeekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m84[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m85[0m[39m:        return aheadToken;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m86[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m87[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m88[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m89[0m[39m:     * Checks if the kind of the next token equals the given one without [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconsuming it.[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m90[0m[39m:     * [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m91[0m[39m:     * @return true if the kind of the next token equals the given one[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m92[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:    public boolean [0m[1;35mpeekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.Kind kind[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m94[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m95[0m[39m:        return aheadToken != null && [0m[1;35maheadToken.getKind[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == kind;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m96[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Analysis Summary[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter comprehensive analysis of the code snippets and evaluation report, I've [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39midentified the root cause of the libFuzzer timeout:[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Root Cause:**[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTwo unbounded while loops in `Type1Parser.java` use a negated compound condition [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpattern that creates performance bottlenecks and potential infinite loops:[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Lines [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[39m in `[0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`**: Searching for [0m[32m"dup"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"readonly"[0m[39m, or [0m[32m"def"[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtokens[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Lines [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[39m in `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`**: Searching for [0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[39m token[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Critical Issues:**[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Infinite loop at EOF**: When `[0m[1;35mpeekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` returns null, `[0m[1;35mpeekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` returns [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfalse, making the negated condition `![0m[1;39m([0m[39mfalse && [0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` = `true`, causing the loop to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontinue indefinitely[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Redundant [0m[1;35mpeekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m calls**: The first loop calls `[0m[1;35mpeekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m times per [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miteration, the second calls it [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m times per iteration, causing severe performance [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdegradation with large inputs[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **No iteration limits**: Unlike other loops in the codebase, these have no [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbounds or safeguards[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Why the patch failed**: The null checks were added AFTER `[0m[1;35mnextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, but [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe timeout occurs due to millions of iterations with redundant `[0m[1;35mpeekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` calls[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mon large fuzzer inputs before reaching EOF[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Fix Strategy[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mI will apply the pattern used successfully in the same file at lines [0m[1;36m555[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m568[0m[39m [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39msearching for [0m[32m"Private"[0m[39m token[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which demonstrates the correct approach for [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munbounded token searches. This pattern:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Stores `[0m[1;35mpeekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in a variable to eliminate redundant calls[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Checks for null BEFORE accessing `[0m[1;35mgetText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Updates the variable after each `[0m[1;35mnextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throws an exception if the expected token is not found[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdditionally, I'll add iteration limits as a safeguard against malformed inputs, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfollowing the pattern used in `XrefParser.java` for loop detection.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Implementation Steps[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix Location [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: Lines [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[39m in `[0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Current problematic code:**[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.NAME[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        && [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"dup"[0m[1;39m)[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                || [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"readonly"[0m[1;39m)[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                || [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"def"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Fix approach:**[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Store `[0m[1;35mpeekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in a variable before the loop[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Change the loop condition to check null explicitly and use positive logic[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Update the variable after each `[0m[1;35mnextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Add an iteration counter with a reasonable limit[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Throw `IOException` if the expected token is not found within the limit[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Transformed pattern:**[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mToken token = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint maxIterations = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m reasonable limit for encoding skip[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint iterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtoken != null && [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtoken.getKind[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == Token.NAME && [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtoken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"dup"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mtoken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"readonly"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mtoken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"def"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++iterations > maxIterations[0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations while searching for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mencoding tokens. Expected 'dup', 'readonly', or 'def'"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    token = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtoken == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unexpected end of file while reading encoding. Expected [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m'dup', 'readonly', or 'def'"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix Location [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Lines [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[39m in `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Current problematic code:**[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.LITERAL[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        && [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Fix approach:**[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Apply the same pattern as Location [0m[1;36m1[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Use a higher iteration limit since the comment indicates variable content may [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mneed to be skipped[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Check for null and throw appropriate exception[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Transformed pattern:**[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mToken token = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint maxIterations = [0m[1;36m50000[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m higher limit as comment indicates variable content[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint iterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtoken != null && [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtoken.getKind[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == Token.LITERAL && [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mtoken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++iterations > maxIterations[0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations while searching for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mCharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    token = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtoken == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unexpected end of file while looking for CharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Justification[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Why this is the optimal approach:**[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Follows established patterns**: Uses the exact pattern from lines [0m[1;36m555[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m568[0m[39m in [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe same file, which successfully handles similar token searches[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Eliminates redundant calls**: Reduces `[0m[1;35mpeekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` calls from [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m to [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m per [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miteration [0m[1;39m([0m[39mLocation [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and from [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m to [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mLocation [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, dramatically improving [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mperformance[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Prevents infinite loops**: Explicitly checks for null before accessing [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mgetText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, preventing the condition from becoming permanently true at EOF[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Adds safeguards**: Iteration limits prevent timeout even with extremely [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmalformed inputs[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Maintains functionality**: Preserves the same logic - skip tokens until [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfinding the expected one[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Provides clear error messages**: Throws descriptive IOExceptions that help [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdebugging[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Preserves existing logic:**[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The loops still skip tokens until finding the expected patterns[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The same tokens are being searched for[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The subsequent code after the loops remains unchanged[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All existing test cases should pass as the functional behavior is identical[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Addresses evaluation report issues:**[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Solves the infinite loop problem when EOF is reached[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Eliminates performance bottleneck from redundant `[0m[1;35mpeekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` calls[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Adds iteration limits to prevent timeout with malicious inputs[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The null checks are now in the correct location [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbefore accessing `[0m[1;35mgetText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Mitigates side effects:**[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The iteration limits [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m and [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are generous enough to handle any [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlegitimate Type [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m font structure[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The IOException messages clearly indicate when limits are exceeded vs when EOF is[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreached[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fix doesn't modify lexer behavior or token generation[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No changes to utility functions or broader codebase[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Reference to similar solutions:**[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Directly mirrors the pattern at lines [0m[1;36m555[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m568[0m[39m in the same file[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Uses iteration limits similar to XrefParser.java loop detection [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m176[0m[1;39m)[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Follows null-check patterns from [0m[1;35mreadSubrs[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m716[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m727[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mreadCharStrings[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m786[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m806[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Code Ranges Used for Fix Strategy[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.jav[0m[1;92ma:217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.jav[0m[1;92ma:640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.jav[0m[1;92ma:555[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m568[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Lexer.jav[0m[1;92ma:71[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m96[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mc[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [95mode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue reports a `libFuzzer: timeout` error, indicating that the fuzzer [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexecution exceeded its time limit while testing the codebase. The patch attempt [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maimed to address the timeout by adding iteration limits to two while loops in the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Type1Parser.java` file, preventing infinite loops by throwing `IOException` after [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma maximum number of iterations or when encountering end-of-file conditions. [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHowever, after applying the patch, the result shows that the timeout error [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpersists, suggesting that the modification did not resolve the underlying [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mperformance issue causing the fuzzer to timeout.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is a timeout error reported by libFuzzer during fuzzing [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moperations. This type of error typically occurs when:[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The code enters an infinite or very long-running loop[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The execution path takes an excessive amount of time to complete[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer-generated input triggers computationally expensive operations[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe error message `ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout` provides minimal detail but clearly [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicates that the execution did not complete within the allocated time budget.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch modifies two locations in the `Type1Parser.java` file within the fontbox [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomponent:[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**First Modification [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m214[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Targets a while loop that searches for encoding tokens [0m[1;39m([0m[32m"dup"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"readonly"[0m[39m, or [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"def"[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Original code used `[0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` repeatedly in the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloop condition[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Patch changes:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Introduces a local `Token token` variable to cache the peeked token[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Adds iteration counter with maximum limit of [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Restructures the loop condition to check for null token and compare token kind [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand text[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Throws `IOException` if maximum iterations exceeded[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Throws `IOException` if null token encountered [0m[1;39m([0m[39munexpected EOF[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Updates the token variable inside the loop after calling `[0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Second Modification [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m637[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Targets a while loop that searches for [0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[39m literal[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Similar transformation to the first modification:[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Caches the peeked token in a local variable[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Adds iteration counter with maximum limit of [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Restructures loop condition to check for null and compare token properties[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Throws `IOException` if maximum iterations exceeded[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Throws `IOException` if null token encountered[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Updates the token variable inside the loop[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Result[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the fuzzer still reports `ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout`, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating that:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The timeout issue persists despite the iteration limits[0m                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m395[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m396[0m[39m:            else[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m397[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m398[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35msb.append[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m399[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m400[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m401[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msb.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m402[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m403[0m[39m:            return null;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m404[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m405[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;35msb.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m406[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Lexer.jav[0m[1;92ma:411[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m427[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m411[0m[39m:    private String [0m[1;35mreadComment[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m413[0m[39m:        StringBuilder sb = new [0m[1;35mStringBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m414[0m[39m:        while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mbuffer.hasRemaining[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m415[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m417[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mc == [0m[32m'\r'[0m[39m || c == [0m[32m'\n'[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
