[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m421[0m[39m:            else[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m422[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m423[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35msb.append[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m424[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m425[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m426[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;35msb.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m427[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Lexer.jav[0m[1;92ma:52[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m65[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m52[0m[39m:    private final ByteBuffer buffer;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m53[0m[39m:    private Token aheadToken;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m54[0m[39m:    private int openParens = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m55[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m56[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m57[0m[39m:     * Constructs a new Type1Lexer given a header-less .pfb segment.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m58[0m[39m:     * @param bytes Header-less .pfb segment[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m59[0m[39m:     * @throws IOException[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m60[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m61[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mType1Lexer[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m62[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m63[0m[39m:        buffer = [0m[1;35mByteBuffer.wrap[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m64[0m[39m:        aheadToken = [0m[1;35mreadToken[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnull[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m65[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.jav[0m[1;92ma:93[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m94[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:        lexer = new [0m[1;35mType1Lexer[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m94[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter carefully examining the code snippets and the evaluation report, I've [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39midentified the root causes of the persistent timeout issue:[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Critical Findings[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **The previous patch only addressed [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m of [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m unbounded scanning loops in [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1Parser**:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Patched: Lines [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39msearching for [0m[32m"dup"[0m[35m/[0m[32m"readonly"[0m[35m/[0m[32m"def"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[39m [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39msearching for [0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Unpatched**: Lines [0m[1;36m226[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m234[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mprocessing [0m[32m"dup"[0m[39m entries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m[1;36m555[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m564[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39msearching[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor [0m[32m"Private"[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **The Type1Lexer has a critical performance bottleneck** that was completely [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muntouched:[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The `[0m[1;35mreadToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m117[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m249[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m has a do-while loop that iterates [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39monce per whitespace/NULL character[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A buffer with thousands of consecutive whitespace or NULL bytes causes [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthousands of iterations[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This happens during lexer initialization [0m[1;39m([0m[39mconstructor line [0m[1;36m64[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m before any [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing begins[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Three [0m[1;35mwhile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m loops in Type1Parser were not addressed**:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `[0m[1;35mreadValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` for arrays [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m395[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m417[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `[0m[1;35mreadProc[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m474[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m497[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `[0m[1;35mreadProcVoid[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m513[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m534[0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Multiple for loops bound by untrusted [0m[32m'length'[0m[39m values** could iterate [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexcessively:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - These loops don't validate length values and could iterate billions of times [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith malicious input[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **The iteration limits in the previous patch [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m and [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are too high** [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor fuzzing purposes and don't prevent timeouts within the fuzzer's budget.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Root Cause[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe timeout is most likely caused by **cumulative delays across multiple layers**:[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Lexer's whitespace skipping loop iterating thousands of times[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Parser's scanning loops calling [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m thousands of times[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Nested structure processing loops [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mwhile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m iterating without limits[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All of these compounding to exceed fuzzer timeout[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: Add Iteration Limit Constants[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd constants to Type1Parser for consistent iteration limits suitable for fuzzing:[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m After line [0m[1;36m45[0m[39m in Type1Parser.java[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_SCAN_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m For token scanning loops[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_NESTING_DEPTH = [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m;     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m For nested structures[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_DICT_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m;     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m For validating length [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalues[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_WHITESPACE_SKIP = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m For lexer whitespace [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhandling[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Fix [0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Whitespace/NULL Handling[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis is the **critical fix** that the previous patch missed. Modify the [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mreadToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method in Type1Lexer.java to limit consecutive whitespace/NULL [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mskipping:[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: Lines [0m[1;36m117[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m249[0m[39m in Type1Lexer.java[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Changes**:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add an iteration counter for the outer do-while loop[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException if too many consecutive whitespace/NULL bytes are encountered[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This prevents the lexer from spending excessive time on malicious inputs filled [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith whitespace[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Implementation**:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Before the do-while loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m119[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, declare: `int skipCount = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- At the start of the do-while body [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m122[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, check: `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++skipCount > [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m10000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Excessive whitespace/NULL bytes"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Reset skipCount to [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m when a non-whitespace/NULL token is processed[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: Fix All Four Scanning Loops in Type1Parser[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Loop [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m**: Lines [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39malready patched but needs lower limit[0m[1;39m)[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Reduce MAX_ITERATIONS from [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m to [0m[1;36m1000[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Loop [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m**: Lines [0m[1;36m226[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m234[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mUN[0m[1;33mPATCH[0m[39mED - critical[0m[1;39m)[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter and limit to [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m iterations[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException if exceeded[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This loop processes [0m[32m"dup"[0m[39m entries and was completely missed by the previous patch[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Loop [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m**: Lines [0m[1;36m555[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m564[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mUN[0m[1;33mPATCH[0m[39mED - critical[0m[1;39m)[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter and limit to [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m iterations[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException if exceeded[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This searches for [0m[32m"Private"[0m[39m token and was missed by previous patch[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Loop [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m**: Lines [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39malready patched but needs lower limit[0m[1;39m)[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Reduce MAX_ITERATIONS from [0m[1;36m50000[0m[39m to [0m[1;36m1000[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m: Add Iteration Limits to [0m[1;35mwhile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Loops[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m**: [0m[1;35mreadValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m array processing [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m395[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m417[0m[1;39m)[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter before [0m[1;35mwhile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check counter at loop start: `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++iterations > MAX_NESTING_DEPTH * [0m[1;36m100[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throw [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException`[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m**: [0m[1;35mreadProc[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m474[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m497[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter before [0m[1;35mwhile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check counter at loop start: `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++iterations > MAX_NESTING_DEPTH * [0m[1;36m100[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throw [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException`[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m**: [0m[1;35mreadProcVoid[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m513[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m534[0m[1;39m)[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter before [0m[1;35mwhile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check counter at loop start: `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++iterations > MAX_NESTING_DEPTH * [0m[1;36m100[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throw [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException`[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m: Validate Length Values in For Loops[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd validation before critical for loops to prevent excessive iterations:[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Locations to validate**:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Line [0m[1;36m109[0m[39m: parseASCII font dict length[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Line [0m[1;36m320[0m[39m: readSimpleDict length[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Line [0m[1;36m572[0m[39m: parseBinary Private dict length[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Line [0m[1;36m709[0m[39m: readSubrs length[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Line [0m[1;36m779[0m[39m: readCharStrings length[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Validation logic**:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || length > MAX_DICT_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid dict length: "[0m[39m + length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m: Add Length Limits to Lexer String Methods[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m**: [0m[1;35mreadComment[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m411[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m427[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter and limit to [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m characters[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException if exceeded[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m**: [0m[1;35mreadRegular[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m379[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m406[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter and limit to [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m characters[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException if exceeded[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m**: [0m[1;35mreadString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m432[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m497[0m[1;39m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter and limit to [0m[1;36m100000[0m[39m characters[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException if exceeded[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Why This Strategy Will Work[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Addresses the root cause**: The lexer's whitespace skipping bottleneck is [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfixed, which was the primary issue missed by the previous patch.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Comprehensive coverage**: All unbounded loops are now protected, not just [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m of[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m scanning loops.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Appropriate limits**: The iteration limits [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m instead of [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m50[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msuitable for fuzzing and realistic fonts.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Layered defense**: Multiple layers of protection prevent any single vector [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom causing timeout:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Lexer-level whitespace limiting[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Parser-level scanning loop limiting[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Nested structure depth limiting[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - For loop length validation[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - String reading length limits[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Preserves existing logic**: All limits are set high enough to handle [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlegitimate Type [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m fonts while preventing malicious inputs from causing timeouts.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **No harness modification**: The fix only modifies Type1Parser.java and [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1Lexer.java, not the fuzzing harness.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Potential Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Legitimate fonts with unusual structure might be rejected**: The limits are [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mset conservatively based on Type [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m font specifications, so this should be rare.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Error messages**: All new exceptions include descriptive messages indicating [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhat limit was exceeded and what was expected.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Backwards compatibility**: Valid fonts will continue to parse correctly since [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe limits are much higher than typical font complexity.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Similar Patterns in Codebase[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe XrefParser [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m95[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m177[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m demonstrates the [0m[32m"lastPrev"[0m[39m pattern for preventing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcircular reference loops. While useful for preventing infinite loops in linked [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstructures, our issue requires iteration counting since we're dealing with [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msequential token scanning and malicious input can have many valid tokens before the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtarget token.[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue reports a libFuzzer timeout error occurring during fuzzing of the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mApache PDFBox fontbox component. A patch was attempted that introduces various [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miteration and length limits throughout the Type1Parser and Type1Lexer classes to [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevent timeout conditions caused by potentially malicious or malformed font files.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDespite applying comprehensive safeguards including maximum iteration limits for [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mscanning, nesting, dictionary lengths, token lengths, comment lengths, and string [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlengths, the patch was unsuccessful - the fuzzer still encounters timeout errors [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mafter the patch is applied.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is a libFuzzer timeout error, which indicates that the fuzzing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocess exceeded the maximum allowed execution time while processing test inputs. [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis typically occurs when the code under test enters into long-running loops or [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mperforms excessive operations, often triggered by specially crafted malicious [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minputs that exploit algorithmic weaknesses or missing bounds checking.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch introduces defensive programming measures across two key files in the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1 font parsing implementation:[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**In Type1Parser.java:**[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Three new constants are defined at the class level:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_SCAN_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m`: Limits scanning operations[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_NESTING_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`: Limits nested structure processing[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_DICT_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`: Limits dictionary length values[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Dictionary length validation [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline ~[0m[1;36m115[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Validates font dictionary length is non-negative and within MAX_DICT_LENGTH[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Throws IOException if validation fails[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Encoding processing loop safeguards [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline ~[0m[1;36m226[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Refactors the token search loop to check token nullability[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds iteration counter `searchIterations` that throws IOException after [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_SCAN_ITERATIONS[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds null check for token after loop completion[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds `dupIterations` counter for the subsequent dup processing loop with same [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_SCAN_ITERATIONS limit[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Simple dictionary length validation [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline ~[0m[1;36m347[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similar validation as font dictionary, checking bounds on dictionary length[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Array processing safeguards [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline ~[0m[1;36m425[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds iteration counter to prevent infinite loops while processing arrays[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Throws IOException after MAX_NESTING_ITERATIONS iterations[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Procedure processing safeguards [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline ~[0m[1;36m509[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds iteration counter to prevent infinite loops while processing procedures[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Throws IOException after MAX_NESTING_ITERATIONS iterations[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**In Type1Lexer.java:**[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Four new constants are defined:[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_WHITESPACE_SKIP = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`: Limits whitespace skipping iterations[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_TOKEN_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m`: Limits individual token length[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_COMMENT_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`: Limits comment length[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_STRING_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m100000[0m[39m`: Limits string length[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Whitespace/NULL byte skipping protection [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline ~[0m[1;36m125[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds `skipCount` variable tracking outer loop iterations[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Throws IOException after MAX_WHITESPACE_SKIP iterations[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Resets counter when regular character is encountered[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Regular token reading protection [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline ~[0m[1;36m393[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds iteration counter to limit token character reading[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Throws IOException after MAX_TOKEN_LENGTH iterations[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Comment reading protection [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline ~[0m[1;36m430[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds iteration counter to limit comment character reading[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Throws IOException after MAX_COMMENT_LENGTH iterations[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. String reading protection [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline ~[0m[1;36m456[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds iteration counter to limit string character reading[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Throws IOException after MAX_STRING_LENGTH iterations[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Result[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch application resulted in the same error: [0m[32m"ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout"[0m[39m. This[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicates that the timeout is not being prevented by the introduced safeguards, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msuggesting one or more of the following scenarios:[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. The timeout occurs in code paths not covered by the added iteration limits[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. The chosen iteration limits are still too high to prevent timeout within the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzer's execution time constraints[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. The timeout occurs in different components or layers of the parsing stack not [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maddressed by this patch[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. There may be additional unbounded loops or recursive operations elsewhere in the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcodebase[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Areas for Further Investigation[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo gain a holistic understanding of the timeout issue, the following areas should [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbe investigated:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Type1Lexer buffer operations**: Examine the ByteBuffer reading operations and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe `[0m[1;35mgetChar[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method to ensure there are no unbounded reads or infinite loops [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhen processing specially crafted buffer content.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Type1Parser encryption/decryption routines**: The constants EEXEC_KEY and [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCHARSTRING_KEY suggest encryption is involved. Review decryption operations that [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmight contain unbounded loops.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Recursive parsing operations**: Look for recursive method calls in Type1Parser[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat could create deep call stacks or exponential time complexity.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Token processing state machine**: Examine the complete token reading state [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmachine in Type1Lexer for edge cases where state transitions might loop [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindefinitely.[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Integration points**: Review how Type1Parser and Type1Lexer are called from [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhigher-level components to identify if timeouts occur during initialization, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcleanup, or other lifecycle operations.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Profiling data**: If available, fuzzer profiling or coverage data would [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicate which specific code paths are being exercised when the timeout occurs.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. **Other parser methods**: Review other methods in Type1Parser not modified by [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis patch, particularly those dealing with font data structures, charstrings, and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msubroutines.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. **Nested structure limits**: While MAX_NESTING_ITERATIONS is set to [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mverify if this is appropriate given the fuzzer's timeout threshold and whether [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnested structures could still cause timeouts.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
