[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m633[0m[39m:                    break;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m634[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m635[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m636[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m637[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m some fonts have [0m[32m"2 index"[0m[39m here, others have [0m[32m"end noaccess put"[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m638[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m sometimes followed by [0m[32m"put"[0m[39m. Either way, we just skip until[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m639[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m the [0m[35m/[0m[95mCharStrings[0m[39m dict is found[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m640[0m[39m:        while [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.LITERAL[0m[1;39m)[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m641[0m[39m:                && [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m642[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m643[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m644[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m645[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m646[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m CharStrings dict[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m647[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.LITERAL, [0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m648[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mreadCharStrings[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlenIV[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m649[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis of the Timeout Issue[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter analyzing the code snippets and evaluation report, I've identified the root [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcauses of the persistent timeout:[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Primary Issues Not Addressed by Previous Patch:[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **[0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Whitespace Loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCRITICAL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: The outer do-while loop [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m120[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m247[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m continues indefinitely when encountering consecutive whitespace or [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNULL bytes. The previous patch added a `skipCount` counter but incremented it [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munconditionally on every outer loop iteration, which could still allow thousands of[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miterations if the buffer contains many whitespace characters interspersed with [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mother content.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Type1Parser Unbounded Scanning Loops**: Three critical scanning loops that [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msearch for specific tokens without bounds:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - [0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m lines [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[39m: Scans for [0m[32m"dup"[0m[35m/[0m[32m"readonly"[0m[35m/[0m[32m"def"[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m lines [0m[1;36m555[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m564[0m[39m: Scans for [0m[32m"Private"[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m lines [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[39m: Scans for [0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The previous patch added iteration limits to some loops but missed these [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcritical scanning operations.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Missing Position Tracking**: No mechanism exists to detect when the parser is [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstuck at the same position [0m[1;39m([0m[39msimilar to the XrefParser pattern[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, allowing potential [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minfinite loops even with high iteration limits.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why Previous Patch Failed:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Limits Too High**: [0m[33mMAX_NESTING_ITERATIONS[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m and [0m[33mMAX_SCAN_ITERATIONS[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mare still too high for fuzzer timeout thresholds [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtypically [0m[1;36m25[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m60[0m[39m seconds[0m[1;39m)[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Incomplete Coverage**: The whitespace loop in Type1Lexer was not properly [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maddressed[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **No Position Tracking**: No detection of stuck parser states[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Scanning Loops Not Fixed**: The three critical unbounded scanning loops in [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1Parser were not addressed at all[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Comprehensive Fix Strategy[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Fix [0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Whitespace Handling[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Lexer.java` [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlines [0m[1;36m117[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m249[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Strategy**:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Track consecutive whitespace/NULL byte skips more carefully[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Reset skipCount only when actual token content is processed[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Lower the MAX_WHITESPACE_SKIP limit significantly [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfrom [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m to [0m[1;36m1000[0m[1;39m)[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add buffer position tracking to detect when stuck at same position[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Implementation**:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Keep the MAX_WHITESPACE_SKIP constant but reduce to [0m[1;36m1000[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Modify the skipCount increment logic to count consecutive outer loop iterations[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Only reset skipCount when the inner while loop processes a non-whitespace, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnon-NULL character that leads to a token return[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The current patch increments skipCount on every outer loop iteration which is [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrect, but the limit is too high[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Add Bounded Scanning with Position Tracking to Type1Parser[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.java`[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Strategy for [0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m192[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m239[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**:[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter AND buffer position tracking[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Reduce MAX_SCAN_ITERATIONS from [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m to [0m[1;36m100[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Track last buffer position to detect stuck state[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException if stuck at same position or exceeded iterations[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Strategy for [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Private search [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m555[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m564[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add NEW iteration limit constant: MAX_TOKEN_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m100[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter to the while loop[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException if exceeded[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This was completely missing from previous patch[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Strategy for [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m CharStrings search [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**:[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter using MAX_TOKEN_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m100[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException if exceeded[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This was completely missing from previous patch[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Reduce All Iteration Limits[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.java` and[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Type1Lexer.java`[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Strategy**:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- MAX_SCAN_ITERATIONS: Reduce from [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m to [0m[1;36m100[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- MAX_NESTING_ITERATIONS: Reduce from [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m to [0m[1;36m1000[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- MAX_DICT_LENGTH: Keep at [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthis is a size limit, not iteration[0m[1;39m)[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- MAX_WHITESPACE_SKIP: Reduce from [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m to [0m[1;36m1000[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- MAX_TOKEN_LENGTH: Reduce from [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m to [0m[1;36m500[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- MAX_COMMENT_LENGTH: Keep at [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcomments can be long[0m[1;39m)[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- MAX_STRING_LENGTH: Keep at [0m[1;36m100000[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mstrings can be long[0m[1;39m)[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add NEW: MAX_TOKEN_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m for scanning loops[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: These limits are still generous for legitimate fonts but prevent [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexcessive iterations that cause timeouts. The nesting depth of [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m is more than [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msufficient for any valid font structure.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Add Position Tracking Pattern [0m[1;39m([0m[39mXrefParser-style[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: Multiple locations in `Type1Parser.java`[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Strategy**:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- For scanning loops, track the lexer's buffer position before and after each [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miteration[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- If position doesn't change between iterations, throw IOException immediately[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This prevents infinite loops even if iteration limits are not reached[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Pattern: Store `lastPosition = [0m[1;35mbuffer.position[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at start, check after each [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mnextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Implementation Points**:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m scanning loop[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Private search loop  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m CharStrings search loop[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Apply All Previous Patch Protections [0m[1;39m([0m[39mReapply with Lower Limits[0m[1;39m)[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: All locations from previous patch[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Strategy**:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Reapply all previous patch iteration limits but with reduced thresholds[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Dictionary length validation [0m[1;39m([0m[39malready in patch[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Encoding dup processing [0m[1;39m([0m[39malready in patch[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - reduce limit[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Array processing [0m[1;39m([0m[39malready in patch[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - reduce limit[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Procedure processing [0m[1;39m([0m[39malready in patch[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - reduce limit[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Token/comment/string reading [0m[1;39m([0m[39malready in patch[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - adjust limits[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Detailed Implementation Steps[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: Update Type1Lexer.java Constants[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLines [0m[1;36m55[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m60[0m[39m: Define constants with reduced limits[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- MAX_WHITESPACE_SKIP = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreduced from [0m[1;36m10000[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- MAX_TOKEN_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m500[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreduced from [0m[1;36m1000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- MAX_COMMENT_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39munchanged[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- MAX_STRING_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m100000[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39munchanged[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Fix [0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Whitespace Handling[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLines [0m[1;36m117[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m249[0m[39m: Modify [0m[1;35mreadToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Keep the skipCount tracking from previous patch[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Reduce MAX_WHITESPACE_SKIP to [0m[1;36m1000[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The current implementation is mostly correct but limit is too high[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: Update Type1Parser.java Constants[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLines [0m[1;36m46[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m51[0m[39m: Define constants with reduced limits[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- MAX_SCAN_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreduced from [0m[1;36m1000[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- MAX_NESTING_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreduced from [0m[1;36m10000[0m[1;39m)[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- MAX_DICT_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39munchanged[0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- MAX_TOKEN_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mNEW constant[0m[1;39m)[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m: Fix [0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Scanning Loop[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLines [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[39m: Already has iteration counter from previous patch[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Reduce MAX_SCAN_ITERATIONS to [0m[1;36m100[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add buffer position tracking:[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Before loop: lastPosition = [0m[1;35mlexer.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mneed to add getter[0m[1;39m)[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - After each [0m[1;35mnextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: check if position == lastPosition, throw if stuck[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Update lastPosition after each iteration[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m: Fix [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Private Search Loop[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLines [0m[1;36m555[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m564[0m[39m: Add iteration counter and position tracking[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add: int searchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add: int lastTokenCount = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrack token count instead of position[0m[1;39m)[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inside loop: if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++searchIterations > MAX_TOKEN_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throw [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Track if making progress between iterations[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m: Fix [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m CharStrings Search Loop[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLines [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[39m: Add iteration counter[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add: int searchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inside loop: if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++searchIterations > MAX_TOKEN_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throw [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m7[0m[39m: Reduce Limits in Array/Procedure Processing[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLines [0m[1;36m392[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m417[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreadValue array[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Already has counter, reduce MAX_NESTING_ITERATIONS[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto [0m[1;36m1000[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLines [0m[1;36m469[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m505[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreadProc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Already has counter, reduce MAX_NESTING_ITERATIONS to [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1000[0m[39m  [0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLines [0m[1;36m510[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m536[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreadProcVoid[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Already has counter, reduce MAX_NESTING_ITERATIONS to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1000[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m: Reduce Limits in Encoding Dup Processing[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLines [0m[1;36m226[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m234[0m[39m: Already has dupIterations counter[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Keep the implementation from previous patch[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Reduce MAX_SCAN_ITERATIONS to [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39malready applied to this counter[0m[1;39m)[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This Approach is Optimal:[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Addresses Root Causes**: Fixes all unbounded loops including the critical [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mscanning operations missed by the previous patch[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Realistic Limits**: The reduced limits [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m100[0m[39m for scanning, [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m for nesting[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mare still generous for legitimate fonts:[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Scanning [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m tokens to find expected keywords is more than sufficient[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Nesting depth of [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m is far beyond any reasonable font structure[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - These limits prevent timeout while allowing valid complex fonts[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Defense in Depth**: Multiple protection layers:[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Iteration counters prevent excessive loops[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Position tracking detects stuck states immediately[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Early termination on null tokens[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Dictionary length validation[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Preserves Existing Logic**: Does not change the parsing algorithm or [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunctionality, only adds bounds checking[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Fuzzer-Friendly**: Lower iteration limits ensure operations complete within [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtypical fuzzer timeout thresholds [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m25[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m60[0m[39m seconds[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Preserves Existing Functionality:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All legitimate fonts have reasonable structure sizes and token counts[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The limits are set high enough to handle complex but valid fonts[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Early exit conditions [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnull checks, EOF checks[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are preserved[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Error messages provide clear diagnostics for malformed fonts[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No changes to token recognition, encoding logic, or decryption[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Addresses Evaluation Report Issues:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Timeout Prevention**: All unbounded loops now have strict iteration limits [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith realistic thresholds[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Complete Coverage**: Addresses all scanning loops, whitespace handling, and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnesting operations[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Stuck Detection**: Position tracking prevents infinite loops even with [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mgenerous limits[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Previous Patch Integration**: Reapplies and improves upon previous protections[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith better limits[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Potential Side Effects and Mitigation:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Extremely Complex Fonts**: Very rare legitimate fonts with deep nesting might [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbe rejected[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: Limits are set conservatively high; can be tuned if needed[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Detection**: Error messages will indicate which limit was exceeded[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Performance Impact**: Additional counter checks and position tracking[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: Negligible overhead [0m[1;39m([0m[39minteger comparisons[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Benefit**: Prevents catastrophic performance degradation from malicious [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minputs[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **[0m[3;91mFalse[0m[39m Positives**: Malformed but benign fonts might be rejected[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: Clear error messages help identify the issue[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Benefit**: Better than timeout/hang on malformed input[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### References to Similar Solutions:[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe position tracking approach is directly inspired by `XrefParser.java` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m176[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m which successfully prevents infinite loops in PDF parsing by tracking the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlast position and detecting when the parser is stuck at the same location. This [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproven pattern is now applied to Type1 font parsing.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue reports a [0m[32m"libFuzzer: timeout"[0m[39m error, indicating that the fuzzer [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mencountered code that took too long to execute, likely due to infinite loops or [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomputationally expensive operations without proper bounds checking. The patch [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mattempt aimed to address this by introducing iteration limits and validation checks[0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvariable `searchIterations` was declared twice within the same method scope [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe issue manifests as [0m[32m"ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout"[0m[39m, which indicates that during [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzz testing, the code execution exceeded the allowed time limit. This typically [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccurs when:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The code enters infinite or near-infinite loops[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- There are unbounded iterations over data structures[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Recursive operations lack proper termination conditions[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Input validation is insufficient, allowing malformed data to trigger expensive [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moperations[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe issue specifically affects the Type1 font parser component in the FontBox [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibrary, as evidenced by the patch location.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt Details[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch introduces several defensive programming measures across two files:[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**In Type1Parser.java:**[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Added constants for iteration limits:**[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_SCAN_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m`: Limit for scanning operations[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_NESTING_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m`: Limit for nested structures [0m[1;39m([0m[39marrays, [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocedures[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_DICT_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`: Maximum allowed dictionary length[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_TOKEN_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m`: Limit for token search operations[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Modified font dictionary parsing [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m107[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Added validation to check if dictionary length is negative or exceeds [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`MAX_DICT_LENGTH`[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Throws `IOException` if validation fails[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Modified encoding parsing [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m214[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Replaced `[0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.NAME[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` check with more explicit null and token [0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Added `searchIterations` counter to limit iterations while searching for [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"dup"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"readonly"[0m[39m, or [0m[32m"def"[0m[39m tokens[0m                                                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Added `dupIterations` counter to limit processing of dup entries[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Modified simple dictionary parsing [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m318[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Added validation for dictionary length similar to font dictionary parsing[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Modified array processing in `[0m[1;35mreadArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m392[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m547[0m[39m:            decrypted = [0m[1;35mdecrypt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes, EEXEC_KEY, [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m548[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m551[0m[39m:            decrypted = [0m[1;35mdecrypt[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mhexToBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, EEXEC_KEY, [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
