[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m534[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m535[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mreadMaybe[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.NAME, [0m[32m"executeonly"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m536[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Overview[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix strategy addresses the [0m[32m"libFuzzer: timeout"[0m[39m error by introducing iteration [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimits and input validation throughout the Type1 font parser. The primary goal is [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto prevent unbounded loops and excessive iterations that can be triggered by [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmalformed or malicious input. Additionally, the compilation error from the [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mduplicate `searchIterations` variable declaration must be resolved.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Core Changes Required[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Add Iteration Limit Constants[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter line [0m[1;36m45[0m[39m in `Type1Parser.java`, add the following constants:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m constants for iteration limits to prevent timeout[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_DICT_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_TOKEN_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_NESTING_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale for values:**[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `MAX_DICT_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`: Prevents excessive memory allocation and loop [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miterations from untrusted dictionary length values. Type [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m fonts typically have [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmuch smaller dictionaries.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `MAX_TOKEN_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m`: Limits token search operations to prevent [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minfinite loops when expected tokens are not found.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `MAX_NESTING_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`: Limits array and procedure processing to handle[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeeply nested structures while accommodating legitimate complex fonts.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Fix Unbounded Token Search Loops[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**A. In `[0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReplace the existing while loop with:[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mToken token = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint searchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtoken != null && [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtoken.getKind[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == Token.NAME && [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtoken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"dup"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mtoken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"readonly"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mtoken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"def"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++searchIterations > MAX_TOKEN_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations searching for encoding [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mtokens"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    token = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtoken == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unexpected EOF while reading encoding"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Critical fix:** The original code has a potential NPE because `[0m[1;35mpeekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` checks[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor null but then immediately calls `[0m[1;35mpeekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` which can NPE. The fix [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexplicitly checks token for null first.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**B. In `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method - First search [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m557[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m564[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReplace the existing while loop with:[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mToken peekToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint privateSearchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpeekToken != null && ![0m[32m"Private"[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mpeekToken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++privateSearchIterations > MAX_TOKEN_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations searching for /Private [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mtoken"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    peekToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**C. In `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method - Second search [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReplace the existing while loop with:[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint charStringsSearchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.LITERAL[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        && [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++charStringsSearchIterations > MAX_TOKEN_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations searching for [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m/CharStrings token"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Key solution to compilation error:** Use unique variable names [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`privateSearchIterations` and `charStringsSearchIterations`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m instead of reusing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`searchIterations`.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Add Iteration Limits to Array Processing[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIn `[0m[1;35mreadValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m395[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m417[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, modify the array processing loop:[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtoken.getKind[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == Token.START_ARRAY[0m[1;39m)[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    int openArray = [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    int iterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++iterations > MAX_NESTING_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations processing array"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            return value;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.START_ARRAY[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            openArray++;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        token = [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mvalue.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtoken[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtoken.getKind[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == Token.END_ARRAY[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            openArray--;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mopenArray == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                break;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Add Iteration Limits to Procedure Processing[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**A. In `[0m[1;35mreadProc[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m474[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m497[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**B. In `[0m[1;35mreadProcVoid[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m513[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m534[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint openProc = [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Validate Dictionary and Array Length Values[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd validation immediately after reading length values from input:[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**A. In `[0m[1;35mparseASCII[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m109[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint length = [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.INTEGER[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.intValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || length > MAX_DICT_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**B. In `[0m[1;35mreadSimpleDict[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m320[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || length > MAX_DICT_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**C. In `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m572[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint length = [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.INTEGER[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.intValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || length > MAX_DICT_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid Private dict length: "[0m[39m + length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**D. In `[0m[1;35mreadSubrs[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m709[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint length = [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.INTEGER[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.intValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || length > MAX_DICT_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid Subrs length: "[0m[39m + length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**E. In `[0m[1;35mreadOtherSubrs[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m759[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint length = [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.INTEGER[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.intValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || length > MAX_DICT_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid OtherSubrs length: "[0m[39m + length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**F. In `[0m[1;35mreadCharStrings[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m779[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint length = [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.INTEGER[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.intValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || length > MAX_DICT_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid CharStrings length: "[0m[39m + length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Justification[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Why this is the optimal approach:**[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Addresses all identified unbounded loops systematically[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Validates untrusted input before using it to control iterations[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Uses reasonable limits that accommodate legitimate fonts while preventing abuse[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Follows existing error handling patterns in the codebase[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Minimal changes to existing logic - only adds defensive checks[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. How it preserves existing logic:**[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All loops maintain their original termination conditions[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Iteration limits are checked in addition to existing conditions, not instead of [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthem[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The parser still handles all valid Type [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m font structures[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Error messages clearly indicate when limits are exceeded for debugging[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Validation occurs before values are used, not after[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**[0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. How it addresses the evaluation report issues:**[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Initial timeout error:** Fixed by limiting all unbounded loops that can be [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtriggered by malicious input[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Compilation error:** Fixed by using unique variable names [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`privateSearchIterations` and `charStringsSearchIterations`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m instead of duplicate [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`searchIterations`[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **NPE risk in [0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:** Fixed by explicitly checking token for null [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbefore accessing `[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**[0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Potential side effects and mitigation:**[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **[0m[3;91mFalse[0m[39m positives on complex fonts:** The limits are set high enough [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m for [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnesting, [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m for searches[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to accommodate legitimate complex fonts while [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreventing abuse[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Breaking legitimate fonts:** The validation only rejects negative or [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexcessively large values. Typical Type [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m fonts have dictionary lengths well below [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m10[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Performance impact:** The iteration counters add minimal overhead [0m[1;39m([0m[39msingle [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minteger increment per iteration[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**[0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Similar patterns in the codebase:**[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The XrefParser in [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/XrefParser.java` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m102[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m176[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muses a `lastPrev` variable to detect and prevent infinite loops in reference chains[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The ScratchFileBuffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m107[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m111[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m validates against Integer.MAX_VALUE before [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39marray operations[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- These demonstrate the codebase's awareness of infinite loop risks and provide [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmodels for defensive programming[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Additional Notes[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe constants defined in `Type1Lexer.java` by the failed patch were not [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimplemented:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_WHITESPACE_SKIP = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_TOKEN_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m500[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_COMMENT_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_STRING_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m100000[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThese are not necessary for this fix because:[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Lexer operations are bounded by buffer size[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The timeout issue is primarily at the parser level, not the lexer level[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Adding these would require more extensive changes to lexer methods without [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproportional security benefit[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix focuses on the parser-level loops which are the primary timeout risk as [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39midentified in the fuzzing results.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
